    "description": {
      "en": {
        "provenance": "imported",
        "value": "Strengthen the capacity of the UNCT on gender equality - including by implementing GTG Capacity Development Plan\r\n\r\nSupport the implementation of UNCT GTG work plan for 2017 (address issue of intersectionality - LGBTI/HIV/disability)\r\n\r\nSupport CSAG to mentor younger GE advocates. Support formation of new CSAG  post a review. Finalise and implement the CSAG Strategy. Organise regular CSAG meetings.\r\n\r\nOrganise consultation for the development of the next strategic note \r\n\r\nSupport strategic partnership and bridging initiatives (LGBTI, HIV, disability issues)\r\n\r\nImplement the NCO communication strategy  to solidify communications approaches, enhance the strategic links between communications, advocacy, resource mobilization and to better capitalize on UN Women’s global communications campaigns online and offline for local advocacy objectives"
      },
